               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnna “Book of the Christening” (fols. 3r-36v)
 
                     Additio 1; colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text I is called Maṣḥafa ṭǝmqat in the incipit (s. <locus target="#5ra">5ra</locus>).</note>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#41va">41va</locus> l.1: ተፈጸመ፡ ዝመጽሐፍ፡ በ፲፻ወ፱፻፳፯፡ ዓ [<locus target="#41vb">41vb</locus> l.1] መተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ይትባረከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ በዳኅና፡
                        ወበሰላም። The note mentions the date 1927 A.M. (= 1934/35 A.D.) as the time of
                        completing the work. </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  
               </msContents>
