                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Careful</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, vivid red</seg>
                        <date>Second half of 20th century</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>ይካ፡ for ይብል፡ ካህን፡</item>
                           <item>ይዲ፡ for ይብል፡ ዲያቆን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipit of Text I; directives to the
                           ministers and their abbreviations; titles of the books to be read;
                           elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals;
                           elements of the quire marks. 
 On the incipit page of Text I (fols.
                           5r), a few groups of lines are rubricated (alternating with black
                           lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#41va">ff. 41va</locus>
                           <desc>l. 4: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#41va">41va</locus> l.4: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወለተ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወአቡሃ፡ ቂሲስ
                              [sic]፡ ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ወእማ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘወሃበቶ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ቀርነ፡ ሰበር፡ ከመ፡
                              ይኵና፡ መርሐ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማይት።[<locus target="#41vb">41vb</locus> l.6] ዘሰረቃ፡
                              ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በስልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ {ወጳውሎስ}፡ ለይኩን፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note is written in a secondary hand. It mentions the donor
                              Walatta Giyorgis, her father Gabra ʾIyasus and her mother Walatta
                              Māryām. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc type="findingAid">A strip of green textile is inserted into the margin
                              of <locus target="#22">fol. 22</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
